   "SSExactMajority/Convergence/DecisionReach.lean:27:0: The module doc-string for a file should be the first command after the imports.\nPlease, add a module doc-string before `/-- Trivial decision phase reachability when `Sout` already holds: every\n`Sswap Ōł® Sout = Stim = IsConsensusConfig` configuration is its own\nwitness with `t = 0`. -/\ntheorem decision_reaches_consensus_when_Sout [Inhabited (Fin n ├Ś Fin n)] {trank Rmax : ŌäĢ}\n    {rankDelta : AgentState n ├Ś AgentState n ŌåÆ AgentState n ├Ś AgentState n} {C : Config (AgentState n) Opinion n}\n    (hC : InSswap C) (hOut : InSout C) :\n    Ōłā (╬│ : DetScheduler n) (t : ŌäĢ), IsConsensusConfig (execution (protocolPEM n trank Rmax rankDelta) C ╬│ t) :=\n  by\n  refine Ō¤©fun _ => default, 0, ?_Ō¤®\n  refine { allSettled := hC.allSettled, ranks_inj := hC.ranks_inj, input_rank := hC.input_rank, allAnswerCorrect := ?_ }\n  exact hOut`.\n\nNote: This linter can be disabled with `set_option linter.style.header false`",
